" Vroom
"
" Run specs or cucumber features with ,t run only the test under the cursor
" with ,T also remembers last run test so you can hit it again on non-test
" files to run the last run test
""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
