" sideways.vim
"
" Move parameters around with ,< and ,>
""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
Plugin 'AndrewRadev/sideways.vim'
nnoremap (( :SidewaysLeft<cr>
nnoremap )) :SidewaysRight<cr>

