" Look up words in dash
""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
Plugin 'rizzatti/dash.vim'
nmap <silent> <leader>h <Plug>DashGlobalSearch
nmap <silent> <leader><leader>h <Plug>DashSearch

